==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Childe
<hw>Childe</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A cognomen formerly
prefixed to his name by the oldest son, until he succeeded to his
ancestral titles, or was knighted; <as>as, <ex>Childe</ex>
Roland</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Childed</ent>⟦br⟧
